#########################################

rnaseq_count_matrix.py

Find all count files (from HTSeq or DEXSeq) matching pattern entered by user (there should be one count file
per sample) and create a matrix with one row for each gene and one column for each sample

Usage: /opt/bin/python/ rnaseq_count_matrix.py rootDir patternToSearch outputFileName


Example: 

    /opt/bin/python rnaseq_count_matrix.py /ifs/res/liang/RNASeq/Proj2983_MassagueJ "*htseq.count*" Proj2983_MassagueJ_htseq.count_allSamples.txt

##########################################
